- Consideration of a request for City shirts for the Board of Aldermen.
      Some Aldermen have requested that Staff provide information regarding City of Fenton shirts for the Board. Currently, the City uses Go 2 Imprints to purchase shirts for the Parks and Recreation Department, as they have provided the lowest cost. It is requested that the Board review their shirt selection on their website at www.go2imprints.com, under apparel, so that a budget can be created for the purchase, should the Board choose to do so.

